headline.main: ITALIANS FALL BACK; Central Defense Line of Fascisti Reported to Have Collapsed DRIVE ALONG COAST GAINS Greeks Penetrate to Positions Above Delvino--Troops Also Push On in Northern Area

lead_paragraph: ATHENS, Tuesday, Dec. 3--The collapse of Italy's central defense line in Albania with the mass surrender of 5,000 Fascist troops was combined with new strategic gains in the south near the coast to precipitate another disorganized Italian retreat on the 100-mile front, a Greek Government spokesman said early today.
